 \r\nAnd you never were \r\n\r\nHigh again \r\nLosing sleep \r\nAnd staying stoned \r\nStoned \r\nLaying low \r\n\r\nTry to fill your time \r\nWith girls that \r\nLeave you cold \r\nKnowing that \r\nThe game is growing old \r\nAgain \r\n\r\nSleepless nights and endless fights \r\nYou're the one that she's begun to \r\n\r\nLove to hate \r\nYeah, she loves to hate you \r\nDo you hate that you still love her? \r\nYour favorite friend, your secret lover \r\n\r\nLove to hate \r\nYeah, she loves to hate you \r\nDo you hate that you still love her? \r\nCause you know you're not above her \r\nAnd you never were \r\n\r\nThe tension was thick as the air we couldn't breathe \r\nIn the haze of the sleepless city where we didn't sleep \r\nIt felt like so many other nights \r\nWe gazed at the dancing of a million lights"}]
